OL,3,C'We will sacrifice our lives': The
OL,4,Cgrieving Lebanese who still back
OL,5,CHezbollah
OL,7,FFor the grieving, their deep pain
OL,8,Ffuels a resolve to stand by the group
OL,9,Fdespite the heavy toll of war, ITV
OL,10,FNews Correspondent John Ray reports
OL,12,FIn the midst of escalating violence
OL,13,Fbetween Lebanon and Israel, a growing
OL,14,Fnumber of Hezbollah supporters remain
OL,15,Fsteadfast in their loyalty, even as
OL,16,Fthey endure personal tragedies.
OL,18,FMany have lost family members to
OL,19,FIsraeli airstrikes, yet they continue
OL,20,Fto believe that Hezbollah's resistance
OL,21,Fis the key to ending the conflict.
