OL,3,C'We will sacrifice our lives': The
OL,4,Cgrieving Lebanese who still back
OL,5,CHezbollah
OL,7,FFor the grieving, their deep pain
OL,8,Ffuels a resolve to stand by the group
OL,9,Fdespite the heavy toll of war.
OL,11,F"My family have been killed from the
OL,12,FIsraelis," Housain Hasan told ITV News
OL,13,Ffrom southern Lebanon.
OL,15,FWith no warning to evacuate, the air-
OL,16,Fwar Israel has waged on Lebanon left
OL,17,FHousain's wife, daughter, son and
OL,18,Funcle dead.
OL,20,FBut the missiles have failed to shake
OL,21,Fhis belief in Hezbollah.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
