OL,3,C'We will sacrifice our lives': The
OL,4,Cgrieving Lebanese who still back
OL,5,CHezbollah
OL,7,F"We are proud. I am proud," Housain
OL,8,Fexclaimed.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, Jawad El Saidi, who was dug
OL,11,Fout of the rubble of his home after an
OL,12,Fattack on his home caused it to
OL,13,Fcollapse, said the war will go on for
OL,14,F"as long as it takes".
OL,16,F"We will sacrifice our lives," he
OL,17,Fadded.
