OL,3,C'We will sacrifice our lives': The
OL,4,Cgrieving Lebanese who still back
OL,5,CHezbollah
OL,7,FOn Thursday, Israel stepped up its air
OL,8,Fstrikes in Lebanon, bolstered its
OL,9,Ftroops on the frontline and warned
OL,10,Fmore people to evacuate.
OL,12,FIt comes in response to a blitz by
OL,13,FIran on Tuesday night, which saw
OL,14,Fhundreds of projectiles targeting
OL,15,FIsrael, following a series of rapidly
OL,16,Fescalating attacks between the country
OL,17,Fand Iran and its proxies.
