OL,3,C'We will sacrifice our lives': The
OL,4,Cgrieving Lebanese who still back
OL,5,CHezbollah
OL,7,FMore than 1,500 people have been
OL,8,Fkilled in Lebanon across the past two
OL,9,Fweeks, according to the country's
OL,10,Fhealth ministry, without saying how
OL,11,Fmany were civilians.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Israeli forces and Iran-
OL,14,Fbacked Hezbollah fighters have engaged
OL,15,Fin fighting on the ground in southern
OL,16,FLebanon.
OL,18,FThe Israeli military said nine
OL,19,Fsoldiers were killed in combat on
OL,20,FWednesday.
